  "texts": [
    "Participants were randomly assigned to one of the four UI conditions (PLAIN = 66; EXPOSITIVE = 71; SUGGESTIVE = 78; SUGGESTIVE ++ = 67).",
    "They used their PC or Mac to join our online user study.",
    "All participants who completed the tasks received 400 Japanese yen (approximately $2.75).",
    "On average, the participants finished all tasks within 48 min (median: 43 min).",
    "We measured the task duration, corresponding to the time spent on a decision-making task per theme."
  ],
